    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>In a truss, horizontal struts above the tie beam or above a line joining the feet of the rafters, commonly between the joists at mid-span. In a truss, horizontal struts above the tie beam or above a line joining the feet of the rafters, commonly between the joists at mid-span.</Note_Text>
